{"tid":511556,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)獵殺星期一 銀翼殺手1-2","createTime":"2017-12-27T15:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T20:52:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ed7ccd7a0c293a97a41e4ae1b7870664442ee8","tid":511556,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=68609afa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=fe5fd763\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/be/Seven_Sisters_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbe%2FSeven_Sisters_Poster.jpg&h=ea14574c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/53/Blade_Runner_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F53%2FBlade_Runner_poster.jpg&h=b3260afe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f2/Blade_Runner_2049_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff2%2FBlade_Runner_2049_Poster.jpg&h=ded97a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事設定於不久的將來，由於人口過剩，迫使政府進行大幅度了獨生子女政策，因此全球每個家庭都規定只能有一個孩子。泰倫斯的女兒在產下七胞胎後過世，泰倫斯為了保護這七胞胎孫女，便開始訓練她們保護自己，但都僅限在公寓內。七胞胎的名字是由星期一至星期天來命名，並每天按自己的名字輪流外出..<br />\n<br />\n2.2019年11月的洛杉磯，退職警察瑞克&middot;戴克（Rick Deckard，哈里遜&middot;福特 飾演）被官員蓋夫（Gaff，愛德華&middot;詹姆士&middot;奧莫斯 飾演）截住，蓋夫帶他去見老長官布萊恩（Bryant，麥克&middot;艾密特&middot;沃許 飾演）。身為一名「銀翼殺手」，戴克的工作是追捕被稱為人造人的生化機器人，並令他們「退役」（「殺死」的委婉說法）。布萊恩告訴戴克近來幾位「連鎖六型」（Nexus-6）人造人非法來到地球，他們僅有四年壽命，可能來地球尋求延長生命的方法<br />\n<br />\n3.故事設定於前集的三十年後，LAPD警官「銀翼殺手」K在一次追殺舊型號複製人的過程中挖掘出了一個埋藏已久的重大秘密，這個秘密很可能會使人類與複製人爆發唯有一方能生存的滅絕戰爭，讓K意想不到的是這個祕密與他之間居然有著非比尋常的關聯。K沿著線索一路追尋而遇見了失蹤三十年的前銀翼殺手瑞克&middot;戴克，並試圖從他身上了解所有的真相<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=8db1d7f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3b88ad4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4c41f893c298c94d8199f3cea8a0bea542af18","tid":511556,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cdc7eb4bec8e2c9f1112a3848f1093356ad1f6","tid":511556,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile